# Megalith x402 Token Approval Configuration
# approve.env provides variables to Megalith x402 Token Approver (approve.js)

# ================ Variables

NETWORK=
APPROVER_KEY=
TOKEN=
STARGATE_CONTRACT=
AMOUNT=unlimited

# ================ Notes

## NETWORK
# 56 = BNB Chain Mainnet
# 97 = BNB Chain Testnet

## APPROVER_KEY
# 0x... Private key of the approver (the account that holds the tokens)

## TOKEN
# 0x... Token contract address (the ERC-20 token to approve)

## STARGATE_CONTRACT
# Leave empty to fetch latest from API automatically
# Or manually set: 0x40200001004b5110333e4de8179426971efd034a

## AMOUNT
# "unlimited" = Maximum approval (recommended, one-time approval)
# Or specific amount in natural units: "1000.0"

# ================ Examples
#
# NETWORK=56
# APPROVER_KEY=0x...
# TOKEN=0x...
# STARGATE_CONTRACT=
# AMOUNT=unlimited

# ================ Notes
# - Approval is only needed for standard ERC-20 tokens
# - EIP-3009 tokens don't require approval
# - Leave STARGATE_CONTRACT empty to auto-fetch from x402.megalithlabs.ai/contracts
# - "unlimited" approval means you only approve once per token
